cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.DS 

The paper is about recommender systems, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed algorithm is a machine learning model that involves matrix factorization (cs.LG) and considers pairwise interactions (cs.SI) between users and events. The evaluation of the algorithm is based on real-world datasets, which involves data processing and analysis (cs.CL) as well as experimental design and analysis (cs.DS).
